column5: Chickenhawk, I sent your package out to you on Monday as promissed, looks like they tried to deliver it yesterday but couldn't for some reason. Is there a problem?  Cliff
no haven't received it yet......will let ya knwo tho cliff...thanks again...

There is something wrong Cody, it was in Waterloo as of Wed. according to Canada Post. You should have had it by now, I sent it Express Post and insured. If you don't have it today, I am going to file a claim with Canada Post.
still haven't received the package yet cliff......iunno if you have contacted canada post or not becuz ive been away all weekend but it never showed up on friday....   Hawk
Did you try tracking it with the tracking # I gave you? I will file a claim with them on Monday Morning.  Cliff
said it did not recognize the tracking number.....
Danbo.....do you ever contribute ANYTHING valuable to ANY topic? 3,141 posts....how many are actually useful?
I say..I say Boy..it's a joke..
Why am I not surprised about that.... LOL
i'm always good for a chukle when i see a danbo post hahah
Looks like you have a little fan base of newbie's! That's cute.
